### Next Steps for Deployment

To enable analytics on Vercel:
1. Deploy this code to Vercel using `vercel deploy` or via Git integration
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Project → Analytics → Enable)
3. After deployment, visit the site and verify the `/_vercel/insights/view` request appears in browser Network tab
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard after users visit the site
